  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nManus developed a complete fully functional beta web application for 7d LIFE COACHING implementing a 7-petal Flower of Life chakra-based coaching model. The app features interactive assessments, goal tracking, weekly progress monitoring, and dynamic visualizations. The development included comprehensive backend logic, database schema, frontend flows, and testing coverage with an elegant coaching aesthetic.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser provided a master prompt specification for a life coaching app and requested creation of a fully functional web application implementing the 7d LIFE COACHING Flower of Life model.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nManus built a complete full-stack web application with 7-petal chakra system, automatic scoring, interactive flower visualization, 90-day goal tracking with micro-actions, weekly progress monitoring, comprehensive dashboard, and elegant UI design with chakra colors and animations.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [web_application] 7d LIFE COACHING Beta App — Fully functional web app with chakra-based coaching system, goal tracking, and interactive visualizations\n- [database_schema] Backend Database Design — Complete data structure for users, assessments, goals, and progress tracking\n- [test_suite] Vitest Test Coverage — Comprehensive testing framework for application functionality\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Implemented complete full-stack architecture\n- Used chakra-based 7-petal system with automatic scoring\n- Created interactive flower visualization\n- Built 90-day goal management system\n- Designed elegant coaching aesthetic with glass morphism effects\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Comprehensive specification enabled rapid development\n- Full-stack approach delivered complete functionality\n- Chakra color system created cohesive visual design\nFailed / suboptimal:\n\n- Initial project setup was cancelled and restarted\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Complex coaching model can be effectively digitized\n- Interactive visualizations enhance user engagement\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- Initial project setup required restart\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Add score history charts to petal detail pages\n- Implement reminder notifications for weekly check-ins\n- Create exportable flower visualizations as downloadable images\n---\nUID: qWSRfGwyiBFmcrXZWi1j4G | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0147\n"
